message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper presents a deep learning-based approach for automatic segmentation of lung lobes in CT scans, which falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a progressive dense V-network (PDV-Net) also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the application of the proposed method in medical imaging and diagnosis indicates that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of medical imaging (cs.MED) and neural networks (cs.NEURON).
